pageContext.claim: “A lot of very important things are going to be taking place in space. And I just don t mean going up to the moon and going up to Mars, where we'll be going very soon. We'll be going to Mars very soon.”
pageContext.analysis: NASA’s “Journey to Mars” initiative predates Trump and builds on what Obama did. And in any case, Americans are not expected to be walking on Mars during the four or eight years of the current administration.
